@startuml
!include _theme.puml
left to right direction

title Monitor — C4 Container View
caption Level 2: runtime containers and external dependencies used by the system

actor "Browser User" as User

rectangle "Monitor System" {
  node "Frontend Container\nNext.js 15 / React 18\nlocalhost:3000 in dev" as Frontend
  node "Backend Container\nSpring Boot 4 / Java 21\nlocalhost:8080" as Backend
}

database "Oracle XE\nsource data" as Oracle
node "Debezium / Kafka Connect\nCDC connector" as Debezium
queue "Kafka\nCDC transport" as Kafka
cloud "SMTP / Groupwise" as SMTP

User --> Frontend : Uses dashboard UI
Frontend --> Backend : /api/events/stream\nvia Next rewrite in dev
Backend --> Frontend : SSE comments + named events

Oracle --> Debezium : Change data capture source
Debezium --> Kafka : Publish Debezium envelopes
Kafka --> Backend : Kafka listener consumes topic
Backend --> SMTP : Send CRITICAL email alerts

note right of Frontend
Main frontend responsibilities:
- render dashboard
- maintain EventSource connection
- track connection state via onopen/onerror
- play critical alert sound
end note

note right of Backend
Main backend responsibilities:
- expose GET /api/events/stream
- fan out events through EventBus
- schedule infrastructure polling
- consume CDC events from Kafka
- emit initial and periodic SSE heartbeats
end note
@enduml

